{"tid":586194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【開門見賊】返家驚見賊人正搜掠　獨居婆婆一句話嚇退兩賊","createTime":"2018-03-09T10:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T10:38:21.000Z","uid":127795,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2516771f32abb0cc4d8ff05024612e36d7a084ee","tid":586194,"uid":127795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"深水埗黃竹街21號一幢唐樓發生爆竊案！上午8時許，一名83歲姓黃獨居婆婆外出後返回住所，豈知一開門入屋赫見兩名年約40歲的陌生男子正在單位內大肆搜掠，婆婆大驚問道：「你哋做乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」。兩賊被婆婆撞破後，立即奪門逃走。婆婆隨後在鄰居協助下報警求助，警員接報到場調查，在附近兜截疑人無果。婆婆經初步點算後，發現未有損失。案件列作爆竊，交由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方追緝兩名涉案疑人，為年約40歲男子，均蓄短黑髮，案發時其中一人身穿黑色外套及牛仔褲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/166457?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=contentlink&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F166457%3Futm_campaign%3Dyahooexchange2018%26utm_source%3Dcontentlink%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=bDcA%2BvpgglXda%2FJiIXtek8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=347c4964\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/166457?utm_campaign=yahooexchange2018&amp;utm_source=contentlink&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"2d971dad304f616b584a064b4adf46745b8e531a","tid":586194,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"Hk01"}]}